---
import ProductLayout from "@layouts/ProductLayout.astro";
---

<ProductLayout
  title="The Job Search Script Vault | ClearCareer"
  description="100+ copy-paste scripts for outreach, negotiation, interviews, follow-ups, rejection responses, and more."
  headline="100+ scripts for every awkward,<br />high-stakes moment in your job search."
  subheadline="Stop agonizing over what to say. Every script is copy-paste ready with customization brackets. Cold emails, salary negotiation, interview answers, rejection responses, and resignation letters."
  bullets={[
    "20 cold outreach scripts: emails, LinkedIn DMs, and warm-cold intros",
    "15 follow-up scripts with exact timing for every scenario",
    "15 salary negotiation scripts: countering, deflecting, and walking away",
    "15 networking scripts: informational interviews, referrals, coffee chats",
    "15 interview scripts: TMAY, tough questions, and thank-you emails",
    "10 rejection response scripts that keep doors open",
    "10 resignation and transition scripts",
  ]}
  price="$29 CAD"
  ctaHref="#checkout"
  ctaText="Get the Script Vault"
  guaranteeText="30-day money-back guarantee. No questions asked."
  faq={[
    {
      q: "Won't these sound like templates?",
      a: "No. Each script has [BRACKET] customization fields for your name, company, role, and specifics. They're designed to sound like you wrote them. We include a 'why this works' note for each one so you understand the psychology.",
    },
    {
      q: "I already bought the Cold Outreach Script Pack ($9). Is there overlap?",
      a: "The Script Vault includes everything in the Cold Outreach Pack plus 70+ additional scripts covering salary negotiation, interviews, rejection responses, networking, and resignation. If you already have the Pack, email us and we'll credit your $9.",
    },
    {
      q: "How are the scripts organized?",
      a: "7 categories, each in its own guide: Cold Outreach, Follow-Ups, Salary Negotiation, Networking, Interviews, Rejection Responses, and Resignation/Transition. Jump to whatever you need today.",
    },
    {
      q: "Can I use these scripts in Canada and the US?",
      a: "Yes. The scripts work for any English-speaking market. Salary negotiation scripts include notes for both Canadian and US contexts where relevant.",
    },
    {
      q: "What if the script doesn't match my exact situation?",
      a: "Each script includes a 'when to use' description so you pick the right one. The customization brackets let you adapt the tone and details. For truly unusual situations, our Career Prompt Vault ($9) includes AI prompts that generate custom scripts.",
    },
  ]}
>
  <Fragment slot="preview">
    <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0161EF]">100+</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Copy-paste scripts</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-white p-4">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0161EF]">7</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Categories covered</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-4 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">
      A career coach charges $200+ per hour. One hour of coaching might give you 3-4 scripts. This vault gives you 100+ for $29.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ProductLayout>
